cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper combines machine learning techniques with optimization algorithms to learn a data-driven encoding for solutions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper applies the approach to robotics problems. The paper also uses neural networks, which suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible category. Finally, the paper's focus on optimization and search algorithms suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
